{"tid":1024220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾飾演希特拉的瑞士演員Bruno Ganz今逝世","createTime":"2019-02-16T11:32:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T12:14:32.000Z","uid":8420,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3dc3e8ce515061bd829a35a7d662a49f056337e9","tid":1024220,"uid":8420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T11:32:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5B8X2Z3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5B8X2Z3.png&h=8ae70317&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dAFbbyzpk-8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdAFbbyzpk-8&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L0oInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=a385306e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dAFbbyzpk-8</a><br />\n<br />\nBruno Ganz, Switzerland&rsquo;s best-known actor, has died in Zurich, his management has announced. He was 77.<br />\n<br />\nGanz has played an angel (Wings of Desire), Hitler (Downfall), a grandfather more than once (Heidi and Vitus), a vampire (Nosferatu the Vampyre), a waiter (Bread and Tulips) and many, many other characters.  His roles gained him an international reputation.<br />\n<br />\nGanz was born in Zurich on March 22, 1941. His Swiss father was a mechanic and his mother came from northern Italy. He discovered acting while at school and started his career on stage.<br />\nIn film, he worked with directors such as Werner Herzog, Wim Wenders and Francis Ford Coppola.<br />\nOne of his most famous cinema roles was as Adolf Hitler in the Downfall (Der Untergang), for which he received much critical acclaim.<br />\n<br />\nThe actor received many prizes, among them the most prestigious award for German-speaking actors, the Iffland-Ring, which is held until death.<br />\nLooking back at his long career in an interviewexternal link with the Neue Z&uuml;rcher Zeitung in 2017, Ganz said that it was a gift to have found a career like acting. &quot;I used the time well,&quot; he said. <br />\n<br />\nGanz had been suffering from cancer. His death was announced on Saturday."},{"pid":"56e9d3dffd33eacb5fc198189a99a4c54ada925a","tid":1024220,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T11:34:01.000Z","msg":"Is all Eric <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da313dda022325088da0d87f9c4e7a793dbee35f","tid":1024220,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T11:35:33.000Z","msg":"Sieg Heil!!!"},{"pid":"ec8b9ba80550e96de16728304e6856c9fc6eb2dc","tid":1024220,"uid":87780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T11:36:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01595b918587d96bd01946d1eb66b30cb4808335","tid":1024220,"uid":1865,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T11:39:01.000Z","msg":"Downfall呢套戲好好睇，<br />\n可以留意到好多演員都出現過係其他德軍電影。"},{"pid":"39d8956aecc5ed3e6a81c5facd888954d7968177","tid":1024220,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01595b918587d96bd01946d1eb66b30cb4808335","tid":1024220,"uid":1865,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T11:39:01.000Z","msg":"Downfall呢套戲好好睇，<br />\n可以留意到好多演員都出現過係其他德軍電影。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T11:41:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b77009eea39a0db32b4920871d102efb736e3a1","tid":1024220,"uid":8798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"01595b918587d96bd01946d1eb66b30cb4808335","tid":1024220,"uid":1865,"like":7,"dislike":0,"